Package se.swedenconnect.signservice.protocol.msg

Interface RequestedCertificateAttribute

All Superinterfaces:
CertificateAttributeIdentifier, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultRequestedCertificateAttribute
public interface RequestedCertificateAttribute extends CertificateAttributeIdentifier
Represents a requested certificate attribute. The sign requester states that a given principal attribute should be mapped into a certificate attribute. This class represents how the requirements for certificate attributes are represented.
